```json
{
"application": "GreatSPN",
"software_requirements": [
"Java",
"Perl",
"GNU Make",
"GLPK (if Flux Balance is enabled)",
"G++ (for compiling C++ code)"
],
"resource_requirements": [
"GreatSPN binaries",
"PN2ODE binary"
],
"additional_notes": [
"The script assumes the existence of a `great_package.sh` file.",
"The `GREATSPN_BINDIR` and `GREATSPN_SCRIPTDIR` environment variables must be set to the appropriate directories.",
"The script requires a `.net` file (specified as the first argument) defining the Petri net model.",
"The script creates temporary files in a directory generated with `mktemp`."
]
}
```
